WEBVTT

00:04:59.480 --> 00:05:02.160
You need to make sure that you have never paid a penny of interest

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.280
to the credit card company,

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.800
and have reaped all the benefits of credit cards.

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:09.640
However, even if these deadbeats take all the money

00:05:09.640 --> 00:05:12.280
and never owe

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:16.600
money, credit card companies still have ways to make money.

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:20.440
One is to charge a handling fee from merchants, which is

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:23.880
generally between 1.5% and 3%.

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:27.560
For example, if a restaurant has a turnover of 1 million, a

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:32.040
2.5% handling fee is about 25,000 yuan.
